{"tid":2295391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【政府新指引】性交時勿面對面 以防感染新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-11-21T18:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T12:13:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d0f821b8f81d905d16ef9e31559fee6365902f","tid":2295391,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2020/11/Apps_600x350_2020-11-20_120340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2020%2F11%2FApps_600x350_2020-11-20_120340.jpg&h=b7a50c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島綜合報道】多倫多巿府公布疫情下性行為新指引，包括如何在睡房內減少病毒傳播，新指引中一個較明顯的方法是選擇毋須面對面接觸的性行為方式。<br />\n<br />\n據多倫多巿政府建議：「要富創意，並尋求方式，尤其是與一位非同居伴侶發生性行為時。」<br />\n<br />\n新指引強調：「在性行為前及後都要洗手，無論當自己獨處或與伴侶一起。」當然，別用未洗的手觸摸自己眼睛、鼻子和口部。<br />\n<br />\n卑詩省則建議其他避免直接接觸的方法，包括運用更多富創意的「洞」，如Glory Holes或隔牆性接觸，以減少親密的面對面接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2020/11/2020-11-20_132941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2020%2F11%2F2020-11-20_132941.jpg&h=c8a68aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多倫多巿指引稱：「一個安全而享受性愛的生活是對心理健康和福祉重要的一部分。不過，最安全的性行為是你可與自己、你同居的人或一個網上伴侶進行。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4618645/2020-11-20/news-%e3%80%90%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e6%96%b0%e6%8c%87%e5%bc%95%e3%80%91%e6%80%a7%e4%ba%a4%e6%99%82%e5%8b%bf%e9%9d%a2%e5%b0%8d%e9%9d%a2++%e4%bb%a5%e9%98%b2%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e7%97%85%e6%af%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4618645%2F2020-11-20%2Fnews-%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%258c%2587%25e5%25bc%2595%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2580%25a7%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%258b%25bf%25e9%259d%25a2%25e5%25b0%258d%25e9%259d%25a2%2B%2B%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e9%2598%25b2%25e6%2584%259